59    protected function writeDrawingRelations(AbstractSlideAlias $pSlideMaster, XMLWriter $objWriter, int $relId)
60    {
61        if ($pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->count() > 0) {
62            // Loop trough images and write relationships
63            $iterator = $pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
64            while ($iterator->valid()) {
65                if ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile || $iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd) {
66                    // Write relationship for image drawing
67                    $this->writeRelationship(
68                        $objWriter,
69                        $relId,
70                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
71                        '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename())
72                    );
73                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
74                    ++$relId;
75                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
76                    // Write relationship for chart drawing
77                    $this->writeRelationship(
78                        $objWriter,
79                        $relId,
80                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
81                        '../charts/' . $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename()
82                    );
83                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
84                    ++$relId;
85                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof Group) {
86                    $iterator2 = $iterator->current()->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
87                    while ($iterator2->valid()) {
88                        if ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile ||
89                            $iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd
90                        ) {
91                            // Write relationship for image drawing
92                            $this->writeRelationship(
93                                $objWriter,
94                                $relId,
95                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
96                                '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename())
97                            );
98                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
99                            ++$relId;
100                        } elseif ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
101                            // Write relationship for chart drawing
102                            $this->writeRelationship(
103                                $objWriter,
104                                $relId,
105                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
106                                '../charts/' . $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename()
107                            );
108                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
109                            ++$relId;
110                        }
111                        $iterator2->next();
112                    }
113                }
114                $iterator->next();
115            }
116        }
117
118        return $relId;
119    }

121    /**
122     * @param array<int, AbstractShape>|ArrayObject<int, AbstractShape> $shapes
123     * @param int $shapeId
124     */
125    protected function writeShapeCollection(XMLWriter $objWriter, $shapes = [], &$shapeId = 0): void
126    {
127        if (0 == count($shapes)) {
128            return;
129        }
130        foreach ($shapes as $shape) {
131            // Increment $shapeId
132            ++$shapeId;
133            // Check type
134            if ($shape instanceof RichText) {
135                $this->writeShapeText($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
136            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeTable) {
137                $this->writeShapeTable($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
138            } elseif ($shape instanceof Line) {
139                $this->writeShapeLine($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
140            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeChart) {
141                $this->writeShapeChart($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
142            } elseif ($shape instanceof AbstractGraphic) {
143                $this->writeShapePic($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
144            } elseif ($shape instanceof AutoShape) {
145                $this->writeShapeAutoShape($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
146            } elseif ($shape instanceof Group) {
147                $this->writeShapeGroup($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
148            } elseif ($shape instanceof Comment) {
149            } else {
150                throw new UndefinedChartTypeException();
151            }
152        }
153    }

160    protected function writeShapeText(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape, int $shapeId): void
161    {
162        // p:sp
163        $objWriter->startElement('p:sp');
164        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr
165        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvSpPr');
166        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr\p:cNvPr
167        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
168        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
169        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
170            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', 'Placeholder for ' . $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
171        } else {
172            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
173        }
174        // Hyperlink
175        if ($shape->hasHyperlink()) {
176            $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $shape);
177        }
178        // > p:sp\p:nvSpPr
179        $objWriter->endElement();
180        // p:sp\p:cNvSpPr
181        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvSpPr');
182        $objWriter->writeAttribute('txBox', '1');
183        $objWriter->endElement();
184        // p:sp\p:cNvSpPr\p:nvPr
185        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
186            $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
187            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
188            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
189            if (null !== $shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx()) {
190                $objWriter->writeAttribute('idx', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx());
191            }
192            $objWriter->endElement();
193            $objWriter->endElement();
194        } else {
195            $objWriter->writeElement('p:nvPr', null);
196        }
197        // > p:sp\p:cNvSpPr
198        $objWriter->endElement();
199        // p:sp\p:spPr
200        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
201
202        if (!$shape->isPlaceholder()) {
203            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
204            $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
205            $objWriter->writeAttributeIf(0 != $shape->getRotation(), 'rot', CommonDrawing::degreesToAngle((int) $shape->getRotation()));
206            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:off
207            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
208            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
209            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
210            $objWriter->endElement();
211            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:ext
212            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
213            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
214            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
215            $objWriter->endElement();
216            // > p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
217            $objWriter->endElement();
218            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom
219            $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
220            $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'rect');
221
222            // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom\a:avLst
223            $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
224
225            $objWriter->endElement();
226        }
227        $this->writeFill($objWriter, $shape->getFill());
228        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
229        $this->writeShadow($objWriter, $shape->getShadow());
230
231        // > p:sp\p:spPr
232        $objWriter->endElement();
233        // p:txBody
234        $objWriter->startElement('p:txBody');
235        // a:bodyPr
236        //@link :http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/documentformat.openxml.drawing.bodyproperties%28v=office.14%29.aspx
237        $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
238        if (!$shape->isPlaceholder()) {
239            $verticalAlign = $shape->getActiveParagraph()->getAlignment()->getVertical();
240            if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
241                $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
242            }
243            if (RichText::WRAP_SQUARE != $shape->getWrap()) {
244                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', $shape->getWrap());
245            }
246            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
247            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getHorizontalOverflow()) {
248                $objWriter->writeAttribute('horzOverflow', $shape->getHorizontalOverflow());
249            }
250            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getVerticalOverflow()) {
251                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vertOverflow', $shape->getVerticalOverflow());
252            }
253            if ($shape->isUpright()) {
254                $objWriter->writeAttribute('upright', '1');
255            }
256            if ($shape->isVertical()) {
257                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', 'vert');
258            }
259            $objWriter->writeAttribute('bIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetBottom()));
260            $objWriter->writeAttribute('lIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetLeft()));
261            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetRight()));
262            $objWriter->writeAttribute('tIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetTop()));
263            if (1 != $shape->getColumns()) {
264                $objWriter->writeAttribute('numCol', $shape->getColumns());
265                $objWriter->writeAttribute('spcCol', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getColumnSpacing()));
266            }
267            // a:spAutoFit
268            $objWriter->startElement('a:' . $shape->getAutoFit());
269            if (RichText::AUTOFIT_NORMAL == $shape->getAutoFit()) {
270                if (null !== $shape->getFontScale()) {
271                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontScale', $shape->getFontScale() * 1000);
272                }
273                if (null !== $shape->getLineSpaceReduction()) {
274                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('lnSpcReduction', $shape->getLineSpaceReduction() * 1000);
275                }
276            }
277            $objWriter->endElement();
278        }
279        $objWriter->endElement();
280        // a:lstStyle
281        $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
282        if ($shape->isPlaceholder() &&
283            (Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ||
284                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_DATETIME == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType())
285        ) {
286            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');
287            $objWriter->startElement('a:fld');
288            $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $this->getGUID());
289            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', (
290                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? 'slidenum' : 'datetime'
291            ));
292            $objWriter->writeElement('a:t', (
293                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? '<nr.>' : '03-04-05'
294            ));
295            $objWriter->endElement();
296            $objWriter->endElement();
297        } else {
298            // Write paragraphs
299            $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $shape->getParagraphs());
300        }
301        $objWriter->endElement();
302        $objWriter->endElement();
303    }

310    protected function writeShapeTable(XMLWriter $objWriter, ShapeTable $shape, int $shapeId): void
311    {

323        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvGraphicFramePr');

329        $objWriter->endElement();
330        // p:graphicFrame/p:nvGraphicFramePr/p:nvPr
331        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
332        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
333            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
334            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
335            $objWriter->endElement();
336        }
337        $objWriter->endElement();
338        // p:graphicFrame/p:nvGraphicFramePr/
339        $objWriter->endElement();

343        $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
344        $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
345        $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
346        $objWriter->endElement();
347        // p:graphicFrame/p:xfrm/a:ext
348        $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
349        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
350        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
351        $objWriter->endElement();
352        // p:graphicFrame/p:xfrm/
353        $objWriter->endElement();
354        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic
355        $objWriter->startElement('a:graphic');
356        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData
357        $objWriter->startElement('a:graphicData');
358        $objWriter->writeAttribute('uri', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/table');
359        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl
360        $objWriter->startElement('a:tbl');
361        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblPr
362        $objWriter->startElement('a:tblPr');
363        $objWriter->writeAttribute('firstRow', '1');
364        $objWriter->writeAttribute('bandRow', '1');
365        $objWriter->endElement();
366        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid
367        $objWriter->startElement('a:tblGrid');
368        // Write cell widths
369        $countCells = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
370        for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
371            //  p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/a:gridCol
372            $objWriter->startElement('a:gridCol');
373            // Calculate column width
374            $width = $shape->getRow(0)->getCell($cell)->getWidth();
375            if (0 == $width) {
376                $colCount = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
377                $totalWidth = $shape->getWidth();
378                $width = $totalWidth / $colCount;
379            }
380            $objWriter->writeAttribute('w', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($width));
381            $objWriter->endElement();
382        }
383        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/
384        $objWriter->endElement();
385        // Colspan / rowspan containers
386        $colSpan = $rowSpan = [];
387        // Default border style
388        $defaultBorder = new Border();
389        // Write rows
390        $countRows = count($shape->getRows());
391        for ($row = 0; $row < $countRows; ++$row) {
392            // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tr
393            $objWriter->startElement('a:tr');
394            $objWriter->writeAttribute('h', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getRow($row)->getHeight()));
395            // Write cells
396            $countCells = count($shape->getRow($row)->getCells());
397            for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
398                // Current cell
399                $currentCell = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell);
400                // Next cell right
401                $hasNextCellRight = $shape->getRow($row)->hasCell($cell + 1);
402                // Next cell below
403                $hasNextRowBelow = $shape->hasRow($row + 1);
404                // a:tc
405                $objWriter->startElement('a:tc');
406                // Colspan
407                if ($currentCell->getColSpan() > 1) {
408                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('gridSpan', $currentCell->getColSpan());
409                    $colSpan[$row] = $currentCell->getColSpan() - 1;
410                } elseif (isset($colSpan[$row]) && $colSpan[$row] > 0) {
411                    --$colSpan[$row];
412                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('hMerge', '1');
413                }
414                // Rowspan
415                if ($currentCell->getRowSpan() > 1) {
416                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('rowSpan', $currentCell->getRowSpan());
417                    $rowSpan[$cell] = $currentCell->getRowSpan() - 1;
418                } elseif (isset($rowSpan[$cell]) && $rowSpan[$cell] > 0) {
419                    --$rowSpan[$cell];
420                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vMerge', '1');
421                }
422                // a:txBody
423                $objWriter->startElement('a:txBody');
424                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr
425                $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
426                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', 'square');
427                $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
428                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/a:spAutoFit
429                $objWriter->writeElement('a:spAutoFit', null);
430                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/
431                $objWriter->endElement();
432                // a:lstStyle
433                $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
434                // Write paragraphs
435                $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $currentCell->getParagraphs());
436                $objWriter->endElement();
437                // a:tcPr
438                $objWriter->startElement('a:tcPr');
439                $firstParagraph = $currentCell->getParagraph(0);
440                $firstParagraphAlignment = $firstParagraph->getAlignment();
441
442                // Text Direction
443                $textDirection = $firstParagraphAlignment->getTextDirection();
444                if (Alignment::TEXT_DIRECTION_HORIZONTAL != $textDirection) {
445                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', $textDirection);
446                }
447                // Alignment (horizontal)
448                $verticalAlign = $firstParagraphAlignment->getVertical();
449                if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
450                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
451                }
452
453                // Margins
454                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginLeft()));
455                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginRight()));
456                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marT', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginTop()));
457                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marB', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginBottom()));
458
459                // Determine borders
460                $borderLeft = $currentCell->getBorders()->getLeft();
461                $borderRight = $currentCell->getBorders()->getRight();
462                $borderTop = $currentCell->getBorders()->getTop();
463                $borderBottom = $currentCell->getBorders()->getBottom();
464                $borderDiagonalDown = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalDown();
465                $borderDiagonalUp = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalUp();
466                // Fix PowerPoint implementation
467                if ($hasNextCellRight) {
468                    $nextCellRight = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell + 1);
469                    if ($nextCellRight->getBorders()->getRight()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()) {
470                        $borderRight = $nextCellRight->getBorders()->getLeft();
471                    }
472                }
473                if ($hasNextRowBelow) {
474                    $nextRowBelow = $shape->getRow($row + 1);
475                    $nextCellBelow = $nextRowBelow->getCell($cell);
476                    if ($nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getBottom()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()) {
477                        $borderBottom = $nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getTop();
478                    }
479                }
480                // Write borders
481                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderLeft, 'L');
482                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderRight, 'R');
483                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderTop, 'T');
484                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderBottom, 'B');
485                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalDown, 'TlToBr');
486                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalUp, 'BlToTr');
487                // Fill
488                $this->writeFill($objWriter, $currentCell->getFill());
489                $objWriter->endElement();
490                $objWriter->endElement();
491            }
492            $objWriter->endElement();
493        }
494        $objWriter->endElement();
495        $objWriter->endElement();
496        $objWriter->endElement();
497        $objWriter->endElement();
498    }
499
500    /**
501     * Write paragraphs.
502     *
503     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
504     * @param array<Paragraph> $paragraphs
505     */
506    protected function writeParagraphs(XMLWriter $objWriter, array $paragraphs, bool $bIsPlaceholder = false): void
507    {
508        // Loop trough paragraphs
509        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
510            // a:p
511            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');
512
513            // a:pPr
514            if (!$bIsPlaceholder) {
515                // a:pPr
516                $objWriter->startElement('a:pPr');
517                $objWriter->writeAttribute('algn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getHorizontal());
518                $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtl', $paragraph->getAlignment()->isRTL() ? '1' : '0');
519                $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontAlgn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getVertical());
520                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginLeft()));
521                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginRight()));
522                $objWriter->writeAttribute('indent', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getIndent()));
523                $objWriter->writeAttribute('lvl', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel());
524
525                // a:pPr:a:lnSpc
526                $objWriter->startElement('a:lnSpc');
527                if ($paragraph->getLineSpacingMode() == Paragraph::LINE_SPACING_MODE_POINT) {
528                    $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
529                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getLineSpacing() * 100);
530                    $objWriter->endElement();
531                } else {
532                    $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPct');
533                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getLineSpacing() * 1000);
534                    $objWriter->endElement();
535                }
536                // >a:pPr:a:lnSpc
537                $objWriter->endElement();
538
539                $objWriter->startElement('a:spcBef');
540                $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
541                $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getSpacingBefore() * 100);
542                $objWriter->endElement();
543                $objWriter->endElement();
544
545                $objWriter->startElement('a:spcAft');
546                $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
547                $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getSpacingAfter() * 100);
548                $objWriter->endElement();
549                $objWriter->endElement();
550
551                // Bullet type specified?
552                if (Bullet::TYPE_NONE != $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
553                    // Color
554                    // a:buClr must be before a:buFont (else PowerPoint crashes at launch)
555                    if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor() instanceof Color) {
556                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buClr');
557                        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor());
558                        $objWriter->endElement();
559                    }
560
561                    // a:buFont
562                    $objWriter->startElement('a:buFont');
563                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletFont());
564                    $objWriter->endElement();
565
566                    if (Bullet::TYPE_BULLET == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
567                        // a:buChar
568                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buChar');
569                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('char', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletChar());
570                        $objWriter->endElement();
571                    } elseif (Bullet::TYPE_NUMERIC == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
572                        // a:buAutoNum
573                        $objWriter->startElement('a:buAutoNum');
574                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStyle());
575                        if (1 != $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt()) {
576                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('startAt', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt());
577                        }
578                        $objWriter->endElement();
579                    }
580                }
581
582                $objWriter->endElement();
583            }
584
585            // Loop trough rich text elements
586            $elements = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
587            foreach ($elements as $element) {
588                if ($element instanceof BreakElement) {
589                    // a:br
590                    $objWriter->writeElement('a:br', null);
591                } elseif ($element instanceof Run || $element instanceof TextElement) {
592                    // a:r
593                    $objWriter->startElement('a:r');
594
595                    // a:rPr
596                    if ($element instanceof Run && !$bIsPlaceholder) {
597                        // a:rPr
598                        $objWriter->startElement('a:rPr');
599
600                        // Lang
601                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('lang', ($element->getLanguage() ? $element->getLanguage() : 'en-US'));
602                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isBold(), 'b', '1');
603                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isItalic(), 'i', '1');
604                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isStrikethrough(), 'strike', 'sngStrike');
605                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('sz', ($element->getFont()->getSize() * 100));
606                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('spc', $element->getFont()->getCharacterSpacing());
607                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('u', $element->getFont()->getUnderline());
608                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSuperScript(), 'baseline', '300000');
609                        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSubScript(), 'baseline', '-250000');
610
611                        // Color - a:solidFill
612                        $objWriter->startElement('a:solidFill');
613                        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $element->getFont()->getColor());
614                        $objWriter->endElement();
615
616                        // Font
617                        // - a:latin
618                        // - a:ea
619                        // - a:cs
620                        $objWriter->startElement('a:' . $element->getFont()->getFormat());
621                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $element->getFont()->getName());
622                        $objWriter->endElement();
623
624                        // a:hlinkClick
625                        $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $element);
626
627                        $objWriter->endElement();
628                    }
629
630                    // t
631                    $objWriter->startElement('a:t');
632                    $objWriter->writeCData(Text::controlCharacterPHP2OOXML($element->getText()));
633                    $objWriter->endElement();
634
635                    $objWriter->endElement();
636                }
637            }
638
639            $objWriter->endElement();
640        }
641    }

643    /**
644     * Write Line Shape.
645     *
646     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
647     */
648    protected function writeShapeLine(XMLWriter $objWriter, Line $shape, int $shapeId): void
649    {
650        // p:sp
651        $objWriter->startElement('p:cxnSp');
652        // p:nvSpPr
653        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvCxnSpPr');
654        // p:cNvPr
655        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
656        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
657        $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
658        $objWriter->endElement();
659        // p:cNvCxnSpPr
660        $objWriter->writeElement('p:cNvCxnSpPr', null);
661        // p:nvPr
662        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
663        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
664            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
665            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
666            $objWriter->endElement();
667        }
668        $objWriter->endElement();
669        $objWriter->endElement();
670        // p:spPr
671        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
672        // a:xfrm
673        $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
674        if ($shape->getWidth() >= 0 && $shape->getHeight() >= 0) {
675            // a:off
676            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
677            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
678            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
679            $objWriter->endElement();
680            // a:ext
681            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
682            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
683            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
684            $objWriter->endElement();
685        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0 && $shape->getHeight() < 0) {
686            // a:off
687            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
688            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
689            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
690            $objWriter->endElement();
691            // a:ext
692            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
693            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
694            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
695            $objWriter->endElement();
696        } elseif ($shape->getHeight() < 0) {
697            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
698            // a:off
699            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
700            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
701            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
702            $objWriter->endElement();
703            // a:ext
704            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
705            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
706            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
707            $objWriter->endElement();
708        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0) {
709            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
710            // a:off
711            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
712            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
713            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
714            $objWriter->endElement();
715            // a:ext
716            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
717            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
718            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
719            $objWriter->endElement();
720        }
721        $objWriter->endElement();
722        // a:prstGeom
723        $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
724        $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'line');
725
726        // a:prstGeom/a:avLst
727        $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
728
729        $objWriter->endElement();
730        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
731        $objWriter->endElement();
732        $objWriter->endElement();
733    }

735    /**
736     * Write Shadow.
737     */
738    protected function writeShadow(XMLWriter $objWriter, Shadow $oShadow): void
739    {
740        if (!($oShadow instanceof Shadow)) {
741            return;
742        }
743
744        if (!$oShadow->isVisible()) {
745            return;
746        }
747
748        // a:effectLst
749        $objWriter->startElement('a:effectLst');
750
751        // a:outerShdw
752        $objWriter->startElement('a:outerShdw');
753        $objWriter->writeAttribute('blurRad', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($oShadow->getBlurRadius()));
754        $objWriter->writeAttribute('dist', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($oShadow->getDistance()));
755        $objWriter->writeAttribute('dir', CommonDrawing::degreesToAngle((int) $oShadow->getDirection()));
756        $objWriter->writeAttribute('algn', $oShadow->getAlignment());
757        $objWriter->writeAttribute('rotWithShape', '0');
758
759        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $oShadow->getColor(), $oShadow->getAlpha());
760
761        $objWriter->endElement();
762
763        $objWriter->endElement();
764    }

766    /**
767     * Write hyperlink.
768     *
769     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
770     * @param AbstractShape|TextElement $shape
771     */
772    protected function writeHyperlink(XMLWriter $objWriter, $shape): void
773    {
774        if (!$shape->hasHyperlink()) {
775            return;
776        }
777        // a:hlinkClick
778        $objWriter->startElement('a:hlinkClick');
779        $objWriter->writeAttribute('r:id', $shape->getHyperlink()->relationId);
780        $objWriter->writeAttribute('tooltip', $shape->getHyperlink()->getTooltip());
781        if ($shape->getHyperlink()->isInternal()) {
782            $objWriter->writeAttribute('action', $shape->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
783        }
784
785        if ($shape->getHyperlink()->isTextColorUsed()) {
786            $objWriter->startElement('a:extLst');
787            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
788            $objWriter->writeAttribute('uri', '{A12FA001-AC4F-418D-AE19-62706E023703}');
789            $objWriter->startElement('ahyp:hlinkClr');
790            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:ahyp', 'http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/drawing/2018/hyperlinkcolor');
791            $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', 'tx');
792            $objWriter->endElement();
793            $objWriter->endElement();
794            $objWriter->endElement();
795        }
796
797        $objWriter->endElement();
798    }

800    /**
801     * Write Note Slide.
802     */
803    protected function writeNote(Note $pNote): string
804    {
805        // Create XML writer
806        $objWriter = new XMLWriter(XMLWriter::STORAGE_MEMORY);
807
808        // XML header
809        $objWriter->startDocument('1.0', 'UTF-8', 'yes');
810
811        // p:notes
812        $objWriter->startElement('p:notes');
813        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:a', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main');
814        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:p', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main');
815        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xmlns:r', 'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships');
816
817        // p:notes/p:cSld
818        $objWriter->startElement('p:cSld');
819
820        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree
821        $objWriter->startElement('p:spTree');
822
823        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr
824        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvGrpSpPr');
825
826        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:cNvPr
827        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
828        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', '1');
829        $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
830        $objWriter->endElement();
831
832        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:cNvGrpSpPr
833        $objWriter->writeElement('p:cNvGrpSpPr', null);
834
835        // p:notes/p:cSld/p:spTree/p:nvGrpSpPr/p:nvPr
